# District Qualification Data

A list of qualification data from every district played between 2009 and
2024. Every item in the list is a dataframe, and each dataframe has at
least the columns "red1", "red2", "red3", "blue1", "blue2", "blue3",
"red_score", and "blue_score". Generated by scripts/get_district_quals.R

## Usage

``` r
dquals24
```

## Format

An object of class `list` of length 827.
